metadata.name: Humanoids X Ranchy R Charity Piece
metadata.description:
In recent times there have been an unexcpetional amount of gun violence, we want to get rid of it completely. This piece is a charity piece meaning that we will start a bid and the highest bidder gets the piece. 100% of the amount that we receive will be donated to the everytown charity, everytown.org
for more information about what this money will go towards and about the charity it will all be on the site above! Thank you for bidding on the official Humanoids x Ranchy R collab
